<chapter xml:id="transformations" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Linear Transformations</title>

<!-- Objectives -->
    <objectives>
            <ul>
                <li> Understand linear transformations both algebraically and graphically.</li>
                <li> Be able to perform basic matrix operations.</li>
                <li> Be able to connect ideas about one-to-one and onto transformations with systems of equations.</li>
                <li> Be able to connect ideas about kernels and images with null spaces and column spaces.</li>
                <li> Be able to calculate orthogonal projections onto a subspace.</li>
                <li> See how to use a computer algebra system to help perform basic operations and apply linear algebra to data analysis in a basic way.</li>
            </ul>
    </objectives>


